fields.name: Guiness 0.0 Alcohol Free Stout - 4 x 440ml
fields.description: Enjoy the same beautifully smooth taste, perfectly balanced flavour and unique dark colour of Guinness Draught. Savour the same dark, ruby red liquid and creamy head, hints of chocolate and coffee, smoothly balanced with bitter, sweet and roasted notes.

fields.name: Corona Cero Alcohol Free 0.0% - 4 x 330ml
fields.description: Offering moderate malty and grainy aromas, with slight fruity and citrussy notes, the lower calorie beer caters for consumers looking for a refreshing and non-alcoholic option without compromising on taste.

fields.name: Old Mout Berries & Cherries 0.05% x 500ml
fields.description: A translucent sunset red, Old Mout Berries & Cherries is warm, deep and sweet.  Enjoy a summery burst of fruits of the forest in the aroma. There’s a special blend of strawberry and raspberry with notes of blueberry and it’s all finished off with a refreshing burst of juicy apple.

fields.name: Brothers Toffee Apple Cider 0.0% x 500ml
fields.description:
Made by 4 brothers in Somerset. They have used there years of knowledge and joy of experimenting with amazing flavour combinations to formulate a new Alcohol Free Toffee Apple flavoured cider.

Experience the rich taste of apples mixed with a nostalgic toffee sweetness right from the first sip.

Toffee Apple Alcohol Free is a blend of cream soda and smouldering toffee with a rich creamy finish. Bring out your curiosity. Serve chilled over ice.

fields.name: McGuigan Sauvignon Blanc 0% x 750ml
fields.description: Generous aromas of gooseberry and citrus fruits, with a subtle grassy tone. This refreshing full flavoured Sauvignon Blanc delivers flavours of passionfruit and lime while finishing clean and crisp.

fields.name: Carl Jung Rosé Wine 0.5% x 70cl
fields.description:
A beautiful pink alcohol free wine with a fresh fizzy taste. Nice strawberry aromas with a medium finish.

Served chilled it is a perfect summer drink. With a delicate fruit flavour; goes well with your favourite cheese.

fields.name: Gordons Gin 0.0% x 70cl
fields.description: Great taste from Gordon’s. New Gordon’s 0.0% provides the bold, piney juniper led character you’d expect from Gordon’s. Gordon’s 0.0% delivers a truly authentic, vibrant non-alcoholic experience that captures the spirit of Gordons perfectly.Just like your usual Gordon’s and tonic, pour 50ml over ice with your chosen tonic and garnish, then stop for a moment and enjoy! Or why not include in your favourite mocktail?

fields.name: Three Spirit Social Elixir 1 x 50cl
fields.description:
Three Spirits Social Elixir is dark, bittersweet and curious. An alcohol free spirit powered by plants.

It’s a dark herbal elixir to enhance your night.

fields.body: By far my favourite alcohol free beverage! Tastes just like the real thing! Top marks!
I liked this alot. Would recommend.
I like it. Would try again.
Very tasty! Will defo be buying again.
